478
00:27:30,609 --> 00:27:32,639
Di mana Ayah?

479
00:27:33,679 --> 00:27:34,810
Apa?

480
00:27:39,080 --> 00:27:40,580
Aku tidak yakin.

481
00:27:40,580 --> 00:27:43,090
Aku harus pamer kepada Ayah.

482
00:27:44,689 --> 00:27:45,689
Tentang apa?

