00:27:45,689 --> 00:27:49,689
Guruku memujiku karena presentasiku baik.

484
00:27:49,689 --> 00:27:51,189
Presentasi macam apa?

485
00:27:51,189 --> 00:27:53,959
Aku pergi ke depan kelas dan membicarakan cita-citaku.

486
00:27:53,959 --> 00:27:55,100
Benarkah?

487
00:27:55,169 --> 00:27:56,669
Kamu bilang apa?

488
00:27:56,669 --> 00:27:58,500
