563
00:33:09,409 --> 00:33:10,879
"Halo. Hai. Ayam!"

564
00:33:10,879 --> 00:33:14,379
Selamat datang kembali, semuanya.

565
00:33:14,550 --> 00:33:17,850
Apa kamu baru, Songha King?

566
00:33:17,850 --> 00:33:19,990
Selamat datang. Semoga kita sering bertemu.

567
00:33:20,290 --> 00:33:23,159
