654
00:39:33,069 --> 00:39:34,100
Semangat!

655
00:39:34,939 --> 00:39:36,009
Semangat!

656
00:39:42,339 --> 00:39:45,310
Lihat? Sudah kuduga kamu menyukai Dae Han.

657
00:39:45,709 --> 00:39:46,750
Terserah.

658
00:39:47,279 --> 00:39:49,020
Aku melihat Da Jung.

659
00:39:49,520 --> 00:39:52,089
Karena kini punya adik yang cantik seperti dia,

660
00:39:53,919 --> 00:39:55,290
