661
00:39:57,729 --> 00:40:01,399
Kamu tidak bisa terus begini kepadaku.

662
00:40:08,870 --> 00:40:10,870
"Rumah Sakit Sunghan"

663
00:40:13,080 --> 00:40:16,080
